((First off I want to apologies to a friend who asked me OOC to help in the 
battle at the before CF it started but I dishonored our friendship by 
chaseing a sword first. Sorry))

::WildWing::
"Liono the maximals at the CF are getting Creamed they need our help." 
WildWing watches the battle over the Cats Eye Network.

::Void::
"WildWing I have some things I want you to take to the Cats to have field 
tested Bluestinger or Key return here to monitor the battle."

::WildWing::
WildWing picks up the duffel bag Exits Cats Lair heading Vector 04.

::Liono::
Liono puts the Spark Reaver in its sheath "We are on our way. Claws out 
cats."  Liono headed  LA2.

::Lilly/Key/Dark/Rinoa/Koj/Inu/Tiamat/::
The rest of the Wild C.A.T.S all climb in the shuttle as they are cramed in 
Bluestinger takes the helm while Liono and the Rest come up with one of my 
crazy.

::Koj::
"What kinda plan is that? Thinks about it "Fine. I'm in" As koj downloads 
Liono's data "What all I'm getting is trust my instincts. Whats next trust 
the matrix to save us all." Koj getting alittle upset.

::Liono::
"Sometimes crazy works! The grand stream was one of my Crazy plans and it 
worked. Trust the matrix is line 13. I gotten us this far and if all else 
fails run like hell line 14. All power to thrusters lets go meet WildWing."

::LA2::
The LA2 takes off leaving at top speed heading for earth a few clicks away 
from CF.
